calamares-settings-foundry-linux (1.0.24) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Hide the swap chooser in the partition page and force no-swap.
    userSwapChoices was [] (empty) which Calamares treats as "unconfigured" and
    backfills with its built-in choices (none + suspend) — so a swap dropdown
    appeared despite the intent. A single-entry list (- none) leaves nothing to
    choose, so Calamares hides the combo box. initialSwapChoice stays "none".

